1.	Software Pre-requisite for Angular Project (latest)
a.	Angular CLI: 17.0.9        
b.	Node: 20.10.0
c.	Package Manager: npm 10.2.5
d.	Git: git version 2.43.0.windows
e.	Visual Studio Code
f.	


2.	Create basic/ empty project/ application using angular CLI
a.	ng new my-first-project
b.	cd my-first-project
c.	npm install
d.	ng serve


3.	How to add bootstrap UI framework to Angular project via CDN
a.	In index.html, Add style sheet link of min.css in head
b.	Add jquery min,  bootstrap min.js in body before <app-root>
c.	Links:
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" crossorigin="anonymous" >
</head>
<body>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <app-root></app-root>
</body>
d.	Html Ex.:
<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Primary</button>


