6.	work to Angular project via NPM
a.	npm i bootstrap@5.3.2
b.	add CSS import in Style.css
@import "..//node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css"

OR
c.	add CSS import in angular.json
"styles": [
              "node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css",
              "src/styles.scss"
            ],



