Mono-Frontend
1)	Documents >
ng new ang-monorepo-project --create-application false --skip-tests
	 
2)	Documents > ang-monorepo-project > projects 
ng g app dashboard
 
3)	Documents > ang-monorepo-project > projects
ng g app angular-concepts --skip-tests
 

4)	Add bootstrap framework
a.	npm i bootstrap@5.3.2
b.	"node_modules/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js
c.	"node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css"
5)	Adding run scripts in package.json to run both projects separately on different port
a.	"start:dashboard": "ng serve dashboard -o --port 4201", 
b.	"start:concepts": "ng serve angular-concepts -o --port 4202"
c.	npm run start:concepts
d.	npm run start:dashboard
6)	install bootstrap 
a.	add bootstrap node modules style path in angular.json under both projects jsdon object styles array.























